Utilities for Input of Case Study Funding Opportunity Announcements

Source: R/case_study.R
case_study.Rd

case_study_foa_imat() FOAs for the IMAT program.

case_study_foa_iotn() FOAs for the IOTN program.

case_study_foa_itcr() FOAs for the ITCR program.

Usage

case_study_foa_imat()

case_study_foa_iotn()

case_study_foa_itcr()

Examples
